text:
Dear: Blackpink,

Whether you guys read this or not I want to say thank you. Thank you for being my inspiration. You know that I slowly lost my fashion sense in the arts back then. I hope that you will get whatever you deserve and always take care of yourself. My first and last KPOP group that I stan I always love and support you. Whatever happened. I will stay blinking forever. From the bottom of my heart, I love you, My OT4.

Sincerely yours,
